zLN1hW414Ow.title: 10 Academy Guest Talk - The Building Blocks of Web3 - Yabebal Fantaye
zLN1hW414Ow.description:
The building blocks of blockchain and in particular the necessary ingredients to start writing smart contracts using the Ethereum protocol.

Blockchain technology has been a key innovation of the last decade and has reached more than three trillion US dollars market share. Starting from its use to fuel cryptocurrency, Bitcoin is the first and biggest in market share, to allowing writing smart contracts that enable distributed finance (DeFi) and Decentralised Autonomous Organisation (DAO), it is becoming the technology that will power Web3, a new iteration of the World Wide Web-based on the blockchain, which incorporates concepts including decentralization and token-based economics.
